description: Removes the specified subnets from the set of configured subnets for the load balancer. After a subnet is removed, all EC2 instances registered with the load balancer in the removed subnet go into the OutOfService state. Then, the load balancer balances the traffic among the remaining routable subnets.

parameters.name: LoadBalancerName
parameters.description: The name of the load balancer.

nested_items.name: Subnets
nested_items.description: The IDs of the remaining subnets for the load balancer.
